<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<%- include("partials/head") %>

<body>
    <%- include("partials/nav") %>
    <div class="container">
        <%- include("partials/header") %>
        <div class="row" style="border-radius: 5px;">
            <div class="col-sm-4">
                <img class="card-img-top" src="https://plus.unsplash.com/premium_vector-1731922571927-ac1d331d87e3?q=80&w=2360&auto=format&fit=crop&ixlib=rb-4.0.3&ixid=M3wxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHx8fA%3D%3D" alt="Card image cap">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <p id="user_age"><strong>Age: </strong>
                            <%= details.user_age%>
                        </p>
                        <p id="user_country"><strong>Country: </strong>
                            <%= details.user_country%>
                        </p>
                        <p id="user_city"><strong>City: </strong>
                            <%= details.user_city%>
                        </p>
                    </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-sm-8">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h5 class="card-title">Information</h5>
                    <h6 class="card-subtitle mb-2 text-muted">Card Contact</h6>
                    <p id="user_email"><strong>Email: </strong>
                        <%= user.email %>
                    </p>
                    <p id="user_phone"><strong>Phone: </strong>[Users Phone]</p>
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <h5 class="card-title">User Bio</h5>
                        <p class="card-text" id="user_bio">
                            <%= details.user_bio%>.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <ul class="form-group">
                        <a href="/update/<%= user.user_ID%>" method="GET" class="btn btn-dark">Update Information</a>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <br>
        <div style="border-radius: 5px;">
            <div>
                <ul class="form-group">
                    <a href="#" method="GET" class="btn btn-dark">Audio translater</a>
                </ul>  
            </div> 
            <div>
                <h2>Audio files</h2>
                <p> Below is an assortment of your saved audio files, to select and review. Have fun!</p>
                <br>
            </div>
        </div>
        <br>
    <div class="row-sm-8" style="border-radius: 5px;">
        <div class="row" style="padding: 2rem;">
            <div class="col-sm-4 col-md-6" id="audio_box">
                <div class="p-3 border bg-dark">
                    <div class="card-content">
                        <div class="card bg-dark" id="audio_card">
                            <h4 id="audio_title">Title: [audio.title] </h4>
                            <span>
                                <h5>Chord: Audio.Result</h5>
                            </span>
                            <div class="card-body">
                                <h6>Heading</h6>
                                <p>The words nature and natural are used for all the things that are
                                    normally not made by
                                    humans. Things like weather, organisms, landforms, celestial
                                    bodies and much more are part of
                                    nature cdcsd scsd cscsd c sdcs csdc sdcs dcsd csdd csd csdc dc .
                                    ...</p>
                                <a href="/audios/:audio_id" class="btn btn-light">Select Audio</a>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        </div>    
    </div>
    <%- include("partials/footer") %>


</body>

</html>